{"tid":814591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"🇳🇬 不得不承認，馬雲真係完勝李嘉誠！","createTime":"2018-09-11T10:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T15:32:32.000Z","uid":5549,"like":19,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea8fd47dee76f33c4b06f75f83cb39140c8111d","tid":814591,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"生活：馬雲搵夠錢啦，又做過華人首富，50幾歲就退休，用錢做自己想做野。李嘉誠係工作狂，為搵錢而搵錢，做到咁老先退休。<br />\n<br />\n事業：馬雲做既野改變左全中國人既生活模式。李嘉誠做地產碼頭資源電訊，冇佢一樣有人做。<br />\n<br />\n家庭：唔多講啦，馬雲完勝。<br />\n<br />\n名譽：馬雲國際知名，中國人好崇拜佢。李嘉誠因爲地產霸權好多香港人都唔鍾意佢。"},{"pid":"ab4337265481a18d1aa0d1035571815653446e01","tid":814591,"uid":5549,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"馬雲鍾意功夫，就拍套野自己做主角打勝所有武打明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bc8ea4354a91ea5ea3e91ee1ed84af7afc8071","tid":814591,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"睇完笑到收唔到聲<br />\n留係贏國等入獄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5e516f5c38349d3c99519d323e529e0bb3eb96","tid":814591,"uid":198245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"娛樂：誠哥有力場，成日玩9香港人以為有假放。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 馬雲身體力行拍戲娛樂大眾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e36e76c66167f7458abe375ff3b0d5d06878870","tid":814591,"uid":91673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"有乜好比？ 同樣有錢過你"},{"pid":"57e791cf689a5af7547a182caaabaedf8a753d91","tid":814591,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"😩"},{"pid":"d5ba098f1b3c50c3f0ad28e9948c332917396774","tid":814591,"uid":208074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"不過馬雲做好多社會公益係真，比誠哥